OL,5, Gary Lineker thought he had a "special 
OL,6, agreement" with the BBC's director     
OL,7, general to tweet about refugees and    
OL,8, immigration, his agent has said.       
OL,10,FIn a piece in the New Statesman, Jon   
OL,11,FHolmes has described the crisis talks  
OL,12,Fheld with BBC bosses during last week's
OL,13,Fstand-off.                             
OL,15,FHe said he warned them that suspending 
OL,16,FLineker could be damaging, hours before
OL,17,Fa staff walk-out began.                
OL,19,FThe BBC apologised for the disruption  
OL,20,Fand will review its social media rules.
